---
layout: default
---
%header
  .container
    %h1.text-center M & D
.hero.primary-bg
  .text-center
    %h2{style: "font-size:54px; color:white; padding-top: 50px;"}
      Experienced Design and Development.
    %h3{style: "color:white;"}
      Fast Fixes to Full Features.
    %a{href:"#contact", class: 'btn cta-btn', style: 'margin-top:25px;'}
      Get Started
      %i.fa.fa-chevron-down
.container
  .row
    .col-sm-4
      .content-box
        .icon
          %span.fa-stack.fa-2x
            %i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
            %i.fa.fa-paint-brush.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
        %h4.text-center
          Design
        %p
          Each project starts with a <strong>WIREFRAME</strong>
          so that you don’t waste time or money on unwanted development. Good
          software is about having a clear vision. We’ll get you from
          <strong>IDEA</strong> to <strong>MOCKUP</strong>, ensuring that your
          website or mobile app is a meaningful extension of your business.
    .col-sm-4
      .content-box
        .icon
          %span.fa-stack.fa-2x
            %i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
            %i.fa.fa-code.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
        %h4.text-center
          Develop
        %p
          Our process includes rapid prototyping with <strong>HTML5</strong>,
          <strong>CSS3</strong>, and <strong>JAVASCRIPT</strong>. We also use
          popular tools like <strong>GITHUB</strong> and <strong>ZAPIER</strong>
          so that you always have control over your process. From MVP to
          full-featured, we’ll make sure your business can scale, but without
          breaking the bank in the meantime.

    .col-sm-4
      .content-box
        .icon
          %span.fa-stack.fa-2x
            %i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
            %i.fa.fa-line-chart.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
        %h4.text-center
          Optimize
        %p
          A website is more than just content, it’s a way to
          <strong>ENGAGE</strong> your customers. Let us help
          you identify where to make the most of your business through
          <strong>A/B TESTING</strong>, <strong>LEAD GENERATION</strong>,
          and <strong>CRM AUTOMATION</strong>. Focus on building your
          business, not lengthy software buildouts.
#contact.primary-bg
  .container{style: 'margin-top:50px'}
    .row
      .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
        .pre-well
          %h2
            Let's work together...
          %h5
            You can email us directly, chat us on slack, or preferably fill out the form.
        {% if site.serving %}
          {% assign form_action = site.local_mailbox %}
        {% else %}
          {% assign form_action = site.prod_mailbox %}
        {% endif %}
        %form#contact-form{action: "//formspree.io/{{form_action}}", method: "POST"}
          .well
            %h4 Your Contact Info
            .row
              .col-sm-6
                .form-group
                  %label.control-label Name
                  %input.form-control{name: "name", type: "text"}
              .col-sm-6
                .form-group
                  %label.control-label Email
                  %input.form-control{name: "_replyto", type: "email"}
            .row
              .col-sm-6
                .form-group
                  %label.control-label Phone
                  %input.form-control{name: "phone", type: "tel"}
              .col-sm-6
                .form-group
                  %label.control-label Company
                  %input.form-control{name: "business", type: "text"}
          .well
            %h4 Project Info
            .row
              .col-xs-12
                %label What type of services are you looking for? Check all that apply
                .form-group{id: "projectType"}
                  .row
                    .col-sm-6
                      .checkbox
                        %label
                          %input{type: "checkbox", name: "project_type[]", value: "Web Design"}
                            Web Design / Redesign
                      .checkbox
                        %label
                          %input{type: "checkbox", name: "project_type[]", value: "Web Development"}
                            Web Development / Coding
                      .checkbox
                        %label
                          %input{type: "checkbox", name: "project_type[]", value: "Marketing"}
                            Marketing / SEO
                      .checkbox
                        %label
                          %input{type: "checkbox", name: "project_type[]", value: "Email Automation"}
                            Email Automation
                    .col-sm-6
                      .checkbox
                        %label
                          %input{type: "checkbox", name: "project_type[]", value: "CRM Implementation"}
                            CRM Implementation
                      .checkbox
                        %label
                          %input{type: "checkbox", name: "project_type[]", value: "eCommerce"}
                            eCommerce
                      .checkbox
                        %label
                          %input{type: "checkbox", name: "project_type[]", value: "Search Results"}
                            Search Result / Filters
                      .checkbox
                        %label
                          %input{type: "checkbox", name: "project_type[]", value: "Client Management"}
                            Client Management
            .row
              .col-sm-6
                .form-group
                  %label Project Budget
                  %select.form-control{name: "project_budjet"}
                    %option Less than $2000
                    %option $3000 - $5000
                    %option $6000 - $10,000
                    %option Over $10,000
              .col-sm-6
                .form-group
                  %label Project Timeline
                  %select.form-control{name: "project_timeline"}
                    %option As soon as possible
                    %option Within a month
                    %option Within the quarter
                    %option Undetermined
            .form-group
              %label.control-label Project Details (Optional)
              %textarea.form-control{name: "project_details", rows: "3"}
            %input.btn.btn-success.btn-lg{type: "submit", value: "Submit"}
